channel.title: Account banned for negative credit (need help)
channel.description:
hello, my account was banned for 17 negative days credit, only way i can get it unbanned is if i send in like 8$ but i cannot do that..
so i am wondering, if anyone could get it unbanned for me, we could share the account, it has around 15-20m on it and hes lvl 92 with 88 cooking (am going for 99 if i get unbanned)
you must be trusted a bit, i know someone will help me, I HOPE.
PS: if we share, most things ill be doing is cooking, working on stats, or dueling, but if you want to spend money on it, i dont want it to waste, so spend money carefully.
post if anyone will help me!!
